Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 11
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Tsukune Aono’s new school is filled with vampires and werewolves. How is a human teenager to survive?
Title: ROSARIO + VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 3
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: THE BLEACH, VOL. 33
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: In this romantic comedy, Haruhi, a poor girl at a rich school, is forced to work – as a boy – for the school’s all-male club.
Title: OURAN HIGH SCHOOL HOST CLUB, VOL. 15
Author: Bisco Hatori

Description: Poor Naruto: he must cope with a ninja summit and a target on the back of his good friend, Sasuke.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 49
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Fame, romance and broken hearts. In this installment, Kyoko gets comfortable with her new role, but her costars are not enjoying it.
Title: SKIP BEAT!, VOL. 22
Author: Yoshiki Nakamura

Description: Alice wanders into a very different part of Wonderland in this interpretation of the classic tale. In this new area of the fantasy land, every man is in love with Alice... and firearms.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS, VOL. 5
Author: QuinRose

Description: Princess Mina has set up a haven, off the coast of Japan, for her vampire people, but danger lurks in the form of Lord Ivanovic who wants Mina as his vampire bride.
Title: DANCE IN THE VAMPIRE BUND, VOL. 9
Author: Nozomu Tamaki

Description: Ultimo and Vice are the embodiment of good and evil. What happens when jealousy, and a doom’s day prophesy, comes into play?
Title: ULTIMO, VOL. 3
Author: Hiroyuki Takei and Stan Lee
Contributor: by Hiroyuki Takei and Stan Lee

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 3
Author: Yana Toboso
